com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaDeviceGateway

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaDevice
      • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaDeviceGateway

  • public class AylaDeviceGateway
extends AylaDevice
    Class representing a Gateway. Gateways provide a bridge between their nodes, which appear as devices to the system, and the local network. Any communication between the mobile application and a device node needs to go through a gateway.

    The AylaDeviceGateway class provides mechanisms for interacting with the nodes managed by the gateway, including adding and removing nodes from the system.
